        {
            "title": "日股半日跌逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"caas-body\"><p><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:東京股市下跌;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/東京股市下跌\">東京股市下跌</a>。日經指數半日跌422點，報37705點，跌幅1.11%。</p></div>",
